,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T22:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6a50b8824938124c2b1e2570424b192fa57a99","tid":1995896,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T23:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d7b3029dbc90e393b60f915409ad0da9bd7960","tid":1995896,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb9cba235e718202e31138d92d881f2a03fb70a","tid":1995896,"uid":54564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:15:48.000Z","msg":"就嚟10/05啦<br />\n想大家思想上都進步"},{"pid":"8560a186cae57c01b23ebdc6a47861a0e85e6b71","tid":1995896,"uid":78892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:18:08.000Z","msg":"推,麻煩仲要報埋哨<br />\n好多盲頭烏蠅唔睇哨gp前面有水炮車都仲衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cd1676b8851d15f0f162b18d4a7bc3e46bbd79","tid":1995896,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:35:12.000Z","msg":"屬於香港人嘅書店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2000687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2000687</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1de02920fa9496725945f6ccb792b68b175b5725","tid":1995896,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bbb66d235293e8f27d61898d92b3d6963733956b","tid":1995896,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T19:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9abd067728235f4daa981a0fe816dc390e964b1f","tid":1995896,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T19:47:40.000Z","msg":"推"}],"pinned":{"pid":"2387c72b6edc5d3d6e67b87597b06ab8263c438a","tid":1995896,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T19:52:38.000Z","msg":"就嚟10/05 大家思想上要重新出發<br />\n除咗開遮、帶物資, 出到去仲有好多嘢做<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>推,麻煩仲要報埋哨<br />\n好多盲頭烏蠅唔睇哨gp前面有水炮車都仲衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以幫手報哨 / 睇哨channel做現場消息傳播員<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>同時請大家black bloc得好啲</blockquote><br />\nblack bloc要包實d自己 + 離場要留意提防跟尾狗<br />\n<br />\n記住真係要be water <br />\n唔好掛住撚狗/ 死守/ 陣地<br />\n個人建議做每樣嘢都要一擊即中, 達到目的就要收手<br />\n唔好比機會班狗圍死 人無事下次先可以繼續出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}